'''alata''' in [[Telerin]] means "radiance, glittering reflection".<ref>{{HM|PM}} p.347</ref> 
==Etymology==
It derives from [[primitive Elvish]] form *''[[ñalatâ]]'' from [[Sundocarmë|Root]] [[ÑAL]].
